Ainslie Pryor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ainslie_Pryor 0 Ainslie Pryor (February 21, 1921 – May 27, 1958) was an American actor. He appeared in the films The Girl in the Red Velvet Swing, Ransom!, Walk the Proud Land, Four Girls in Town, The Shadow on the Window, The Guns of Fort Petticoat, The Left Handed Gun, Kathy O' and Onionhead. He appeared in the television series' Ford Star Jubilee, Steve Donovan, Western Marshal, Lux Video Theatre, Front Row Center, You Are There, Medic, Wire Service, Sheriff of Cochise, Meet McGraw, Sugarfoot, Gunsmoke, Suspicion, Cheyenne, Studio One, General Electric Theater, Playhouse 90 and The Adventures of Hiram Holliday.He died of cancer on May 27, 1958, in Hollywood, California at age 37.
